{"tid":2197703,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"特區歡迎香港被評全球最自由經濟體　重申法治核心價值","createTime":"2020-09-10T21:54:41.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-04T10:56:06.000Z","uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":50,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"5976aff47f75ccfefefeab0d9fb9a0abf20abbba","tid":2197703,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-10T21:54:41.000Z","msg":"總部設在加拿大的菲沙研究所，再次將香港評為全球最自由經濟體。特區政府表示歡迎，指報告明確肯定香港一直以來堅定地建立自由經濟體，及提供公平營商環境的決心。<br />\n<br />\n菲沙研究所發表《世界經濟自由度2020年度報告》，根據2018年數據，將香港評為全球最自由經濟體，但指出中國政府在2019及2020年對香港的干預，令財產權的不安全感明顯上升，並正在削弱香港法治，很大機會為香港在法治制度及財產保障的範疇，帶來負面影響。<br />\n<br />\n特區政府發言人回應說，有關推論建基於偏頗及選擇性的評論，以及無理據的不公推測，對此表示遺憾，強調法治是香港的核心價值。<br />\n<br />\n對於報告提及訂立港區國安法及相關執法行動，政府發言人重申，港區國安法是為了堅定不移並全面貫徹一國兩制，保持香港繁榮穩定，並不影響本港居民的合法權利和自由。<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1548981-20200911.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1548981-20200911.htm&d=u5s3JLQ1HZhTjCUFZ9m1FAogPkW5zMkxdNnzPoGklno%3D&h=ca5a3e1f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1548981-20200911.htm&h=fa9fb33d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1548981-20200911.htm</a>"},{"pid":"67d80353f24730acc5b0854575593225b097e525","tid":2197703,"uid":56550,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-10T22:52:46.000Z","msg":"犯國安法啦<br />\n發表報告令人憎恨政府"},{"pid":"b0263d253fb65dd84a1671da8f6d32742266af75","tid":2197703,"uid":70786,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-10T22:54:06.000Z","msg":"輸打贏要<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6fae043db474c2d6a77a5d0e506fde27b4f38ff3","tid":2197703,"uid":5502,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-10T22:54:18.000Z","msg":"根據2018年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f074b926de4bc860f33bc6f83b764dcae5dc4f5e","tid":2197703,"uid":85965,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-10T22:55:24.000Z","msg":"根據2018年數據<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1d218517812f3f545f76c4d7125f02eef8ac50c2","tid":2197703,"uid":108337,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-10T22:57:45.000Z","msg":"投訴到佢收回報告"},{"pid":"b59b7e7646ab9ef0a19d8d7c50a79922853e8602","tid":2197703,"uid":350989,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-10T23:04:48.000Z","msg":"搵藍絲廢老開 po 鬧佢啦 再要迫教育局同學歷評審局唔承認呢個國家呢間大學嘅學位 雖遠必豬呀 中國人民唔係就咁算數牙嘛 大國銳實力去撚左邊呀你老母"},{"pid":"aabb2d71ed4b11b864bf401fd898814c55b3d06e","tid":2197703,"uid":8257,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"f074b926de4bc860f33bc6f83b764dcae5dc4f5e","tid":2197703,"uid":85965,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-10T22:55:24.000Z","msg":"根據2018年數據<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-10T23:42:13.000Z","msg":"姐係下年會大跌 之後fisher 會犯國安法"},{"pid":"625b111a6954130924a15b3bc552e32c581d44b4","tid":2197703,"uid":11291,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-10T23:46:45.000Z","msg":"法治是香港的核心價值<br />\n<br />\n呢句嘢真係笑死人<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n而家嘅香港有撚法治<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e4d4f070843957a365f5b98449b666fff671ed3","tid":2197703,"uid":43062,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-10T23:47:08.000Z","msg":"留名睇19/20 數據<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"500a1df6559c1a9f885ed2f670c72c8245563787","tid":2197703,"uid":41343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-10T23:47:42.000Z","msg":"即係個政府同時稱讚又批評同一份報告？"},{"pid":"1d544c840db8fdbfc8791aa6072c425478c2282a","tid":2197703,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-10T23:52:52.000Z","msg":"總部設在加拿大的菲沙研究所將香港評為最自由經濟體，但警告中國的干預會影響香港未來排名。<br />\n<br />\n負責報告的麥克馬洪認為，香港在經濟領域上仍然是全球最自由，但憂慮來自中國的干預，包括示威鎮壓會削弱香港法治，不利在各個方面確保平等。他又表示，用於評估的數據有兩年滯後，估計未來香港排名的得分將會下跌。<br />\n<br />\n菲沙研究所評估全球162個國家同地區的指標，包括法規、對外貿易自由度、政府規模、支出以及稅收等。<br />\n<br />\n新加坡排第二。新西蘭排第三。美國排第六。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n因為間野講明出年排名一定跌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fbf3d0dfea4ad4bf396e1193d89d35f2390ba047","tid":2197703,"uid":39710,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-10T23:57:57.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"xx-large\">根據2018年數據</span>"},{"pid":"bcbb7eff372736f5bb0e1f2ab79b1f2dcea88702","tid":2197703,"uid":3860,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-11T00:18:15.000Z","msg":"排第一就歡迎<br />\n話你呢兩年會跌就偏頗<br />\n<br />\n點可以做到咁無恥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e8b712367870a77d798cd3fc66a69d8bf5c05030","tid":2197703,"uid":123774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-11T00:19:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/73oogBb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F73oogBb.jpg&h=e96dd984&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9b08e49484e166d30683102368ba58168684fc7a","tid":2197703,"uid":41423,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-11T00:39:56.000Z","msg":"人唔笑狗都吠"},{"pid":"2f6d1ec2d2230763aae8bbe68696072aad83f031","tid":2197703,"uid":290118,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-04T10:56:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}